title: Exclusive Video: These Grandfathered Bloopers Will Make Your Day
text: Exclusive Video: These Grandfathered Bloopers Will Make Your Day Monday, 19 October 2015 (9 minutes ago) There is a pair of babies on the Grandfathered set, but judging from this exclusive blooper reel, the grown-ups might be the ones who break the most. You can place some of the blame on John Stamos , who fails to silence his phone during a scene. Looks like he could use a pep talk from Coach Taylor. Check out the bloopers below. Grandfathered airs Tuesdays at 8/7c on Fox. Other Links From TVGuide.com GrandfatheredJohn StamosJosh PeckPaget Brewster
